c function is advisable.', 'Synergism', 'The use of naltrexone with other potentially hepatotoxic agents should be avoided whenever possible (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/35598/', '[1] "Product Information. ReVia (naltrexone)." DuPont Pharmaceuticals, Wilmington, DE.', 'Amphetamine, Metamfetamine, Lisdexamfetamine, Solriamfetol, Caffeine, Methylphenidate, Dexmethylphenidate, Dextroamphetamine, Armodafinil, Citicoline, Modafinil', 'Oxymorphone, Tapentadol, Meperidine, Butorphanol, Hydromorphone, Dezocine, Opium, Pentazocine, Nalbuphine, Dihydrocodeine, Naloxone, More', 1767369485);
