mic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/35950/', '[1] "Product Information. Clolar (clofarabine)." sanofi-aventis, Bridgewater, NJ.', 'Fluorouracil, Pemetrexed, Mercaptopurine, Cladribine, Trifluridine, Floxuridine, Gemcitabine, Nelarabine, Cytarabine, Pralatrexate, Decitabine, More', 'Tinidazole, Quinacrine, Secnidazole, Furazolidone, Nitazoxanide, Artesunate, Mefloquine, Lumefantrine, Artemether, Pyrimethamine, Hydroxychloroquine, More', 1767369485);
